Chapter.Section:
Philosophy

The package &homalg; is meant to be the first volume of a continuously
growing and opensource book about http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Homological_algebra. &homalg;
is an attempt to translate as much as possible of homological algebra,
as can be found in books like , ,
, ,  and
, into a language that also a computer can
directly understand. Yes, ``also'': &homalg; should, as the above
mentioned books, by a great extent be readable by a human being.
Finding such a language was by no means an easy task (&see;
). For the reasons mentioned below (&see;
) I have chosen &GAP4; as the language of this
book project.
